description: Have fun asking yes or no questions to the magic eight ball and listening to it's predictions.  This is not a real prediction app it is meant for you to have fun.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask magic eight ball will it rain today
Alexa, ask magic eight ball will the knicks win today
Alexa, ask magic eight ball  should I learn to speak spanish
name: Magic Eight Ball
shortDescription: A fun Magic Eight Ball prediction skill.
